snippet.title: Pin Puck Version 1.3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Play now (it's free!): https://patdavisgames.itch.io/pin-puck

Pin Puck version 1.3 is out now! This brand new content update contains a new single player Target Smash mode, alongside new maps for local multiplayer and minor improvements to the game flow.

The music for the game (and the trailer) is by Angus MV Arnold, who you can find at: https://twitter.com/AngusMVArnold

And you can of course find me at:
https://twitter.com/PatDavisGames
